In recent years, the global clove cigarettes market has witnessed a shift towards online sales channels due to changing consumer behavior and preferences. Online sales offer convenience, a wide product selection, and doorstep delivery, appealing to tech-savvy consumers who prefer shopping from the comfort of their homes. E-commerce platforms provide a global reach, enabling clove cigarette manufacturers to target a broader audience and expand their market presence. Offline sales channels, including retail stores, convenience stores, hypermarkets/supermarkets, and other physical retail locations, continue to play a crucial role in reaching traditional consumers who prefer in-person shopping experiences. These offline channels provide visibility to products and allow for direct consumer interactions, fostering brand loyalty and trust.

